snippet.title: Jet de Go! 2 Let's Go By Airliner -  Fukuoka to Naha - PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
Information:-
Jet De Go! 2 is a Japanese made flight simulator for the ps2 later in the year the game is ported to pc. Jet De go! 2 is developed by Taito (A japanese game developing company) Jet de go! 2 is a part of the landing series. The first Jet De Go! was released for the PlayStation, Game Boy Color, PC - February 2000.
=============================
This is the pc port of the game and is very rare to find in these days. I have both versions of the game for the PS2 as well as for the PC, the pc port can be downloaded , I will leave the link to the person who saved the copy form the only site which had the game and for the ps2 version just say that you want it in the comment box.
===========================
